description: Pakal Autochthonous Mexican Cookery is providing the people of Austin with a delicious new dimension to interior Mexican dishes.This talented team is taking fresh ingredients and innovative vessels like baguettes, tortillas, tostadas, and bowls, to serve a tasty selection of taco creations. Next time you have an appetite for cuisine of this caliber, come place an order at Pakal!
name: Pakal Autochthonous Mexican Cookery
